    UI_DASHBOARD -.HTTP REST.-> INFRA_REST
    UI_API --> APP_PLAN
    UI_API --> APP_INTEG
    INFRA_REST --> UI_API

    APP_PLAN --> DOM_CORE
    APP_PLAN --> DOM_HELPERS
    APP_PLAN --> INFRA_PROBE
    APP_JOB --> APP_PLAN
    APP_INTEG --> INFRA_HTTP
    APP_HOOKS --> INFRA_DB

    DOM_QUALITY --> DOM_PERCEPTUAL
    DOM_CORE --> INFRA_HTTP
    DOM_PERCEPTUAL --> INFRA_PROBE

    APP_PLAN --> INFRA_DB
    INFRA_NOTIF -.toast.-> UI_DESKTOP

